174 A.3d 517 NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. J.I., DEFENDANT-PETITIONER, AND L.R., SR., DEFENDANT. IN THE MATTER OF THE GUARDIANSHIP OF L.R., JR., A MINOR-RESPONDENT.

C-144 September Term 2017

079267 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-3457/3458-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
